<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَالإِقَالَةُ فَسْخٌ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- تُسَنُّ لِلنَّادِمِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span class="c5"> الرِّبَا نَوْعَانِ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> رِبَا فَضْلٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَرِبَا نَسِيئَةٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span class="c5"> فَرِبَا الفَضْلِ:</span> يَحْرُمُ فِي كُلِّ مَكِيلٍ وَمَوْزُونٍ بِيعَ بِجِنْسِهِ مُتَفَاضِلاً.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>- وَلَوْ يَسِيراً لَا يَتَأَتَّى.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَيَصِحُّ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- بِهِ مُتَسَاوِياً.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَبِغَيْرِهِ مُطْلَقاً، بِشَرْطِ قَبْضٍ قَبْلَ تَفَرُّقٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>- لَا مَكِيلٍ بِجِنْسِهِ وَزْناً، وَلَا عَكْسُهُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>- إِلَّا إِذَا عُلِمَ تَسَاوِيهِمَا فِي المِعْيَارِ الشَّرْعِيِّ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَرِبَا النَّسِيئَةِ:</span> يَحْرُمُ فِيمَا اتَّفَقَا فِي عِلَّةِ رِبَا فَضْلٍ؛ كَمَكِيلٍ بِمَكِيلٍ، وَمَوْزُونٍ بِمَوْزُونٍ نَسَاءً.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>- إِلَّا أَنْ يَكُونَ الثَّمَنُ أَحَدَ النَّقْدَيْنِ؛ فَيَصِحُّ.<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>